        public int getLevel()
        Method for finding the current level of PokemonData that contain the PokemonExperience object.

        The Switch-Case returns the PokemonData's level based on its experienceTypes and currentExperience. All return statements are casted so that all the level turnouts are truncated. The default case should not be called at any time, otherwise the getLevel will throw a new IllegalStateException. Formula for finding MediumSlow and credited to:
